    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You make an unarmed attack, gaining a +2 bonus to the attack roll, and dealing 1d4 bonus damage per 3 levels (maximum 4d4), which is not multiplied on critical hits. If the attack scored a critical hit, or if the attack roll exceeded the target's massive damage threshold, it is @Condition[dazed;duration=1]{dazed} for 1 round, which can be saved against.<br><br>The attack is so fast that it can't be seen as more than a blur unless the target has High Speed Sight 1 or higher, has an active Speed Rank of 1 or higher, or succeeds at a Spot check opposed by the attack roll.<br><br>If you are not wearing clothing with pockets near the waist, you suffer a -4 penalty to the Perform Requirements.</p>\n\n\n<p><b>Mastery:</b> The fifth step allows the technique to extend to a range 5 ft beyond your reach, provided there are no obstacles between you and the target, and the target does not benefit from any amount of cover.</p>\n",
